Type: Package
Package: easyPlot
Title: An Interactive Interface to ggplot2
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Michal", "Majka", , "michalmajka@hotmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-7524-8014"))
Description: A graphical user interface for ggplot2 which allows the user
    to dynamically create four kind of plots (scatterplots, histograms,
    boxplots and bar charts) and generates a reproducible code.
License: GPL-3 + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/majkamichal/easyPlot
